spec_data.Name: liba52
spec_data.Description:
liba52 is a free library for decoding ATSC A/52 streams. The A/52
standard is used in a variety of applications, including digital
television and DVD. It is also known as AC-3 or AC3
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Mon 07 Aug 2017 12:05:53 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A free ATSC A/52 stream decoder, also known as AC-3 or AC3
